00:01:28,870 --> 00:01:31,860
[Legend of Fuyao]

21
00:01:31,860 --> 00:01:34,600
~ Episode 65 ~

22
00:01:48,050 --> 00:01:49,740
It's Fei Yan.

23
00:01:53,810 --> 00:01:57,030
We've just arrived in Firmament for more than two hours,

24
00:01:57,030 --> 00:02:00,330
yet Illusion Palace has sent out so many scouts.

25
00:02:00,330 --> 00:02:03,020
Fei Yan's intentions are not to be ignored.

26
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,450
I'll go look for my Grand Teacher first.

27
00:02:08,450 --> 00:02:10,450
- I'll go with you.
- No.

28
00:02:10,450 --> 00:02:12,270
Grand Teacher wants to capture you.

29
00:02:12,270 --> 00:02:14,670
I can't let you walk into his net.

30
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:21,510
If I don't go with you, will your Grand Teacher let you off?

31
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:24,830
Wuji, don't you still know me?

32
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:29,880
If you give up your life in exchange for mine,

33
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:32,470
I will never agree to it.

34
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:37,350
I hope that from now on, whatever happens, we can face it together.

35
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:46,600
Just this once, I want you to listen to me.

36
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,890
Although my Grand Teacher is strict,

37
00:02:48,890 --> 00:02:52,590
he's a person that's open-hearted and puts the world as priority.

38
00:02:53,690 --> 00:02:57,490
If he can find a way to resolve this crisis,

39
00:02:57,490 --> 00:02:59,940
he will surely not harm any innocent person.

40
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,800
What if there is no other way?

41
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,530
I will also come up with one.

42
00:03:11,290 --> 00:03:12,750
Okay.

43
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:26,240
If...

44
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:31,030
I'm just saying if.

45
00:03:35,450 --> 00:03:38,330
If that day really comes,

46
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:43,330
I hope that you can personally kill me.

47
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:53,440
And after I die, you must take up the responsibility to protect Five Regions.

48
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:06,180
Let me tell you this.

49
00:04:06,180 --> 00:04:12,570
By the time the Venus Star in the west rises tomorrow, I'll be back.

50
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:16,590
Okay.

51
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:33,430
Say it again that you'll wait for me here.

52
00:04:35,770 --> 00:04:37,530
I'll wait for you.

53
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:43,390
Wait for me.

54
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:46,790
Yes.

55
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:16,760
Evergreen Shrine and your Illusion Palace never had any interaction for hundreds of years.

56
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,860
Palace Leader, you come here in person today.

57
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:21,780
Is there any important matter to instruct?

58
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:23,490
The female demon has entered Firmament.

59
00:06:23,490 --> 00:06:28,070
Tell me. Is that an important matter?

60
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:31,760
In my opinion, we shouldn't delay any minute in capturing the female demon.

61
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:34,640
We should act early.

62
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:41,230
For so many years, Evergreen Shrine has been looking for the female demon to protect the world,

63
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:44,680
but we never mentioned this to Illusion Palace.

64
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:47,340
Today, upon her entering the territory of Firmament,

65
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:52,090
I don't think there's a need for you to ask about it.

66
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:53,350
That's indeed correct.

67
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:59,170
Your Illusion Palace connived with Di Feitian and brought harm to the world in the Firmament Great War that year.

68
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:02,220
Although you eventually stopped before it was too late and suddenly repented on your actions,

69
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:06,490
Firmament will never forget the sins you've committed.

70
00:07:06,490 --> 00:07:08,060
Although what Elder said is reasonable,

71
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:13,430
don't forget that it was our Illusion Palace that suggested to use the Mystic Spirit Leaf to resist the evil sense back then;

72
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:15,540
hence, we were able to turn the tides.

73
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:18,530
In terms of merit, our Illusion Palace naturally had contributed.

74
00:07:18,530 --> 00:07:20,290
You can't—

75
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,860
People walking different paths can't make plans together.

76
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:26,720
That is just normal.

77
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:30,950
But now is the moment that will determine the survival of Five Regions.

78
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:36,490
Shouldn't we let go of past grievances and prioritize the world?

79
00:07:41,330 --> 00:07:47,560
In my knowledge, you have been secretly investigating the whereabouts of the female demon these past years.

80
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:50,860
Could it be you have another intention?

81
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:54,500
If Firmament is safe and sound, my Illusion Palace will be safe and sound.

82
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,770
That is my purpose.

83
00:07:56,770 --> 00:08:00,600
In the past, my Illusion Palace took the wrong path and greatly tainted our reputation.

84
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:05,380
Of course, everything I'm doing now is to make up for the mistakes of my ancestors.

85
00:08:05,380 --> 00:08:10,730
Since the world is in danger, my Illusion Palace should bear a bit of the responsibility to save it.

86
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:13,030
If that's the case, that will be great.

87
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:16,590
It's just that the matter of the female demon is very important.

88
00:08:16,590 --> 00:08:20,720
My Evergreen Shrine has made the appropriate preparations.

89
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:24,630
No need for Palace Leader to worry about it anymore.

90
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:35,750
This Zhangsun Wuji is a member of your Evergreen Shrine.

91
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:40,270
And this Zhangsun Wuji even wants to disregard the lives in Five Regions just to preserve the life of the female demon.

92
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:43,220
Is this the appropriate arrangement of your Evergreen Shrine?

93
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:45,770
You kept refusing the inquiry of my Illusion Palace.

94
00:08:45,770 --> 00:08:52,120
It can't be helped for others to feel that you're trying to harbor your student out of your love for him.

95
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,930
The female demon matter concerns all the lives in this world.

96
00:08:53,930 --> 00:08:56,240
I, Heavenly Secret, will never act out of personal reasons.

97
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,770
Since that's the case,

98
00:08:57,770 --> 00:09:02,160
why is your brilliant student of Evergreen Shrine with that female demon day and night, not separating from each other?

99
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:06,960
He didn't hesitate to be against the laws of Firmament and employ magic to hide their whereabouts.

100
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:09,920
Zhangsun Wuji has known this female demon for a long time.

101
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:13,050
He had a lot of chances to eliminate this source of destruction.

102
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:15,400
But now, not only is she alive,

103
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:19,490
she was even able to break her numerous seals with the help of your Evergreen Shrine.

104
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:21,510
Now, the danger has been made.

105
00:09:21,510 --> 00:09:25,390
The disaster is upon us.

106
00:09:29,850 --> 00:09:34,960
And you knew all about these.

107
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:39,280
How come we never heard Evergreen Shrine mention this?

108
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:45,480
My disobedient student got bewitched by the female demon.

109
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:48,640
I already ordered him to eliminate the source of trouble.

110
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:51,980
I even activated the punishment technique of Firmament.

111
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:56,070
Now, Wuji has personally brought the female demon to Firmament.

112
00:09:56,070 --> 00:10:01,020
May elders give him one more chance and observe what he'll do next.

113
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:05,730
He disobeyed you beforehand, so how can he suddenly have a change of mind now?

114
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:08,960
Aren't you afraid that he'll try to harbor her again?

115
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:13,510
This person is after all the designated heir of Evergreen Shrine

116
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:15,530
and is favored a lot by Palace Leader.

117
00:10:15,530 --> 00:10:19,410
Even if he does have any selfish intentions, I fear that onlookers can't really say anything about it.

118
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:21,190
A bunch of nonsense!

119
00:10:21,190 --> 00:10:23,160
My Evergreen Shrine has always been open and upright.

120
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:28,860
Since our ancestral teacher Chang Qingzi established our palace until now, everything we did was for Five Regions.

121
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:33,480
How can I tolerate you saying such words and being unruly?

122
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,990
I think you misunderstood.

123
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:36,840
I didn't intend to offend you.

124
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:40,160
It's just that Zhangsun Wuji has been bewitched by that female demon.

125
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:43,080
You two have a very deep teacher-student affection for each other.

126
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:46,740
I was afraid that someone will take advantage of that and deceive you.

127
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:49,930
If you get softhearted and become lenient to this disobedient student,

128
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:52,310
not only is that a waste of your lifetime of cultivation,

129
00:10:52,310 --> 00:10:56,510
you will even involve the whole Firmament and Five Regions into it.

130
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:58,830
By then, when the world turns into chaos,

131
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:05,840
your Evergreen Shrine will indeed have to bear a soiled reputation forever.

132
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:17,040
Now is the critical time that will determine the survival of Five Regions,

133
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:20,190
none can go against the will of Heaven.

134
00:11:20,190 --> 00:11:23,430
Although he is my most favored student,

135
00:11:23,430 --> 00:11:28,950
if he really defends that female demon, then that's going against Evergreen Shrine and the world!

136
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:32,590
Of course, I will not indulge him.

137
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:37,190
Palace Leader, it's good if you really have such resoluteness.

138
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:41,290
That will be the great blessings of the Five Regions.

139
00:11:41,290 --> 00:11:47,040
We elders, here in Firmament, can all be at ease too.

140
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:54,500
I'm afraid they still do not understand your wishes, Grand Teacher.

141
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:56,700
Of course, they don't understand.

142
00:11:56,700 --> 00:12:01,600
I want the female demon alive, while they want her dead.

143
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:05,400
These are two different paths.

144
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:07,400
To resurrect Di Feitian,

145
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:11,400
my Illusion Palace has waited and longed for her for 1000 years.

146
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:18,500
How would those rotten Confucians from the Evergreen Shrine understand what I think?

147
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:23,200
If we do not get cooperation from the Evergreen Shrine, then wouldn't we have returned with no gain?

148
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:29,600
Evergreen Shrine is just an old jade building held in high esteem.

149
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,600
To simply make a female demon submit,

150
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:34,500
I do not need to pretend to ask them for help.

151
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:42,700
It's just that Zhangsun Wuji is a hindrance.

152
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:47,200
Him being beside the female demon is big trouble after all.

153
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:53,200
Does Grand Teacher want to borrow Evergreen Shrine's hand to eliminate him?

154
00:12:56,400 --> 00:13:00,400
Zhangsun Wuji is deeply in love with the female demon.

155
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:02,600
He has protected her this whole time.

156
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:06,200
Of course, he wouldn't let the female demon fall into my hands.

157
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,800
I wasted so much breath back there

158
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:12,800
just to force Heavenly Secret to promise the thing that he should be doing.

159
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:15,000
Evergreen Shrine has a disobedient student,

160
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:18,200
so it's just right for Evergreen Shrine to punish him severely.

161
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,800
This way,

162
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:23,900
someone will help me pluck out this bothersome Zhangsun Wuji.

163
00:13:23,900 --> 00:13:26,700
To deal with a small female demon,

164
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:30,340
I have plenty of plans.

165
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,400
You've gone back on your word.

166
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:35,400
You clearly said that if I helped you, you would have a real fight with me.

167
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,830
You are always pestering me.

168
00:13:36,830 --> 00:13:38,800
Is it really only for fighting?

169
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:42,000
- You are really—
- Giving you too much leeway.

170
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,200
Have you had enough?

171
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,800
I hope that when I see you again, you won't be so stubborn.

172
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:50,000
That Fuyao is the person you are looking for!

173
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
Don't appear in front of her again.

174
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:57,800
If you die in her hands in the future, don't blame me for not warning you!

175
00:14:03,570 --> 00:14:05,230
Yan'er?

176
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:09,690
Yes.

177
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:40,700
Yan'er, you must remember that the most useless thing in this world are feelings.

178
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,800
Yes.

179
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:54,800
Evergreen Shrine's student Zhangsun Wuji seeks to meet Grand Teacher.

180
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,400
You've finally returned.

181
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:04,200
Yes, I have returned.

182
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:07,900
Where is that female demon?

183
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:12,300
Fuyao is not a female demon.

184
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:15,300
Up to when do you plan to keep protecting her?

185
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:20,300
Wuji, have you forgotten your status and your mission?

186
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:21,990
I dare not forget it.

187
00:15:21,990 --> 00:15:23,800
It's just that this matter concerns a life.

188
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:27,300
I want to ask Grand Teacher to give Fuyao a chance to live.

189
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:29,100
Disobedient student!

190
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:34,200
It's already at this time and you still are going to defend that female demon?

191
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:38,400
Wuji, you have greatly disappointed me.

192
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:44,400
Based on Firmament's laws, a student who disobeyed the clique's order is considered a traitor

193
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:46,600
and will be dealt with the extreme form of punishment.

194
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:49,400
Since you've forgotten your status,

195
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:52,900
don't blame me for being heartless.

196
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:04,950
I understand.

197
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:09,200
I'm willing to suffer the punishment of Firmament Netherworld Illusion.

198
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:12,300
But it's indicated in the laws of Firmament

199
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:15,100
that surviving the four realms, one can become intangible.

200
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,240
Once the person being punished safely survives it,

201
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:19,100
no matter what his status is,

202
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:24,000
he'll be treated as if coming from the shrine and obtain the promise of help from Evergreen Shrine.

203
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,600
May Grand Teacher

204
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,800
not forget it.

205
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:53,500
You dare to mention the laws of Firmament?

206
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:56,400
Okay. Okay!

207
00:16:57,300 --> 00:16:59,600
You are indeed my good student.

208
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:03,600
Let me see then if your ten years of skills

209
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:07,400
will be able to help you get past the Netherworld Illusion.

210
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,700
Grand Teacher,

211
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,900
excuse me.

212
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:14,600
When the Venus Star rises?

213
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:19,800
By the time the Venus Star in the west rises tomorrow, I'll be back.

214
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:21,800
Yuan Bao.

215
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:25,800
Wuji said that he'd be back when the Venus Star rises.

216
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:29,100
But now, there is still no news from him.

217
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:31,600
Can you allow me to find him?

218
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,800
Yuan Bao,

219
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:40,400
if anything bad happens to Wuji, I won't continue living by myself.

220
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,430
I beg you. I beg you.

221
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:44,300
Take me to find him.

222
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:46,200
Yuan Bao.

223
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,600
Grand Teacher.

224
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,500
I shouldn't have treated you like this.

225
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:26,600
But during harsh times,

226
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:29,600
one can only use harsh methods.

227
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:33,700
Wuji, tell me.

228
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:37,660
Where is the female demon?

229
00:20:42,600 --> 00:20:44,400
Grand Teacher,

230
00:20:46,570 --> 00:20:52,950
our Firmament always says that we have the world in our heart.

231
00:20:52,950 --> 00:20:58,800
But this world must now rely on the life of an innocent woman to be saved.

232
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,830
I'd like to ask you.

233
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:09,640
What's the use for me to cultivate for so many years?

234
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:15,400
What's the use of our Firmament?

235
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:17,200
I won't argue about these with you right now.

236
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:21,200
Say it! Where did you hide her?

237
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:25,700
Grand Teacher, Fuyao isn't a female demon.

238
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:28,900
She's chivalrous and cares about the world.

239
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:32,270
Just because of one five-colored stone, she has to unjustly die?

240
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:33,800
This is unfair!

241
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:36,800
In this world, there's no complete fairness.

242
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:38,400
Maybe...

243
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:42,300
Maybe killing her isn't the only path.

244
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:44,400
In the ancient writings of Firmament,

245
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:47,600
there are a lot of ancient divine powers that have been lost.

246
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:51,200
I only want to earnestly ask Grand Teacher to agree to let me find them.

247
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:53,600
