256
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,200
Disobedient student.

257
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:39,800
You have really forgotten your status.

258
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:43,000
Since the moment I fell in love with her,

259
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:46,400
