265
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,740
I will be around.

266
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:34,200
Even to the point of becoming the enemy of Evergreen Shrine?

267
00:23:35,360 --> 00:23:37,000
Grand Teacher,

268
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:51,360
I'm going to ensure that Fuyao is safe for a lifetime.

269
00:23:55,300 --> 00:24:01,270
My martial arts and power came from Evergreen Shrine.

270
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:10,800
The kindness of Teacher is as vast as a mountain and I dare not forget it.

271
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:15,040
But today, for Fuyao,

272
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:20,400
I must disobey Grand Teacher.

273
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:34,160
I, Wuji, know that my crime is unpardonable.

274
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:43,470
May Grand Teacher just take back my cultivated martial arts skills.

275
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:47,800
