276
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:10,260
This Imprisonment Technique

277
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:13,200
can break all kinds of internal and external energies.

278
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:17,320
My Evergreen Shrine has never used it for more than 700 years.

279
00:25:17,320 --> 00:25:24,060
Wuji, I'm giving you one last chance.

280
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:26,770
Where is the female demon?

281
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:46,150
