307
00:28:21,150 --> 00:28:22,670
I'm very worried about him.

308
00:28:22,670 --> 00:28:24,600
Let's go find him together then.

309
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:26,260
In this Holy Land Firmament,

310
00:28:26,260 --> 00:28:28,990
