325
00:29:35,130 --> 00:29:38,110
Stop...

326
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:39,350
Stop!

327
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:41,130
This is a punishment set up by Grand Teacher.

328
00:29:41,130 --> 00:29:42,670
