347
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:17,750
I know.

348
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,390
Of course, I know.

349
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:25,760
But if I want to earn even a bit of a chance here,

350
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:31,490
this is the only way.

351
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:36,590
You want to...

352
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:42,400
No, you can't... You can't!

353
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:45,820
It's too dangerous! No!

354
00:31:45,820 --> 00:31:48,600
We've learned martial arts techniques of Firmament since we were little.

355
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:52,080
