356
00:31:52,080 --> 00:31:57,800
I must remove this body of skills for me to find a chance to survive.

357
00:31:57,800 --> 00:31:59,890
No, you can't!

358
00:31:59,890 --> 00:32:03,720
If not because...

359
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:07,930
Grand Teacher... Grand Teacher made such a kind of punishment,

360
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:14,530
I fear that...

361
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:23,050
