362
00:32:23,050 --> 00:32:24,920
That method is very dangerous.

363
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:28,200
No one has successfully done it for thousands of years.

364
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:31,340
This is the peak of the heavens.

365
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:35,350
If you remove your lifetime cultivation now, that is equivalent to suicide.

366
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:38,690
You're gambling with your life!

367
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:51,500
Gambling with my life?

368
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:55,130
Trying to preserve Fuyao's life is going against the mandate of Heaven to begin with.

369
00:32:55,130 --> 00:33:00,490
If I am successful, I can be with her in this life.

370
00:33:00,490 --> 00:33:02,660
If I fail,

371
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:07,070
I can die with her,

372
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:12,830
