380
00:34:01,980 --> 00:34:03,870
That is the peak of the heavens.

381
00:34:03,870 --> 00:34:06,510
At such a dangerous place, plus the use of the Exterminating Nails,

382
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:09,310
