394
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:45,290
Presently, we only have that choice.

395
00:34:56,460 --> 00:34:58,160
Stop!

396
00:34:59,810 --> 00:35:02,630
As long as you leave the female demon behind, I can ensure that the others will not live!

397
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:04,010
Older Sis Fuyao, you leave first.

398
00:35:04,010 --> 00:35:06,470
You go to the peak of Mt. Emotionless first. Leave this to us.

399
00:35:06,470 --> 00:35:08,690
