400
00:35:08,690 --> 00:35:11,520
Go first. We'll be there in a while.

401
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:15,400
- Quickly go.
- Believe us.

402
00:36:02,290 --> 00:36:04,020
Thank you!

403
00:36:04,020 --> 00:36:05,750
