407
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:19,010
I finally found this item.

408
00:36:19,010 --> 00:36:22,520
Maybe, it can tell you the perfect method that can fulfill both sides that you want.

409
00:36:24,350 --> 00:36:26,710
There's no use.

410
00:36:26,710 --> 00:36:30,460
This item is the most treasured item of ancestral teacher Chang Qingzi.

411
00:36:30,460 --> 00:36:36,230
Only the student of Evergreen Shrine in its direct line can open it.

412
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:43,510
Are you all right?

413
00:36:48,420 --> 00:36:52,450
In its direct line? Evergreen Shrine's direct student...

414
00:36:52,450 --> 00:36:54,450
Evergreen Shrine?

415
00:36:57,110 --> 00:37:00,050
Blood...

416
00:37:00,050 --> 00:37:03,170
