423
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,760
It...

424
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:34,820
It started with me.

425
00:38:35,470 --> 00:38:37,510
It existed because of me.

426
00:38:41,870 --> 00:38:49,710
