435
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:16,540
Do you understand?

436
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:20,090
You care about my life, her life,

437
00:39:20,090 --> 00:39:22,100
everyone's life!

438
00:39:22,100 --> 00:39:26,220
Why can't you just think for yourself?

439
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:31,780
Why can't you just think for yourself?

440
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:36,510
I never... was a selfless person.

441
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,700
I love Fuyao.

442
00:39:40,700 --> 00:39:44,410
Everything I did was for my own selfish reason,

443
00:39:44,410 --> 00:39:48,560
