444
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:50,710
My life is hanging by a thread.

445
00:39:51,390 --> 00:39:55,290
Come to think of it. Come to think of it.

446
00:39:55,290 --> 00:40:00,970
I did all these for my selfish intentions.

447
00:40:00,970 --> 00:40:06,760
Liking someone is selfish to begin with, isn't it?

448
00:40:07,790 --> 00:40:09,160
It started with me.

449
00:40:09,160 --> 00:40:10,470
It existed because of me.

450
00:40:10,470 --> 00:40:14,960
Since it existed because of me, it will end with me.

451
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:17,260
Since it existed because of me,

452
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,620
it will end with me.

453
00:40:22,690 --> 00:40:24,130
Are you planning to?

454
00:40:24,130 --> 00:40:26,230
Don't! Don't!

455
00:40:26,230 --> 00:40:30,850
If... If from the start,

456
00:40:30,850 --> 00:40:33,620
this is a destined deadlock,

457
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:41,300
if the will of the heavens can't be changed,

458
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:46,410
then I... will die with her.

459
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:49,460
